{"article_id":"ZgbZ3kanv2gabLur","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump says","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he made his point","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"-","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"the U.S. needs a border wall ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"and he will build it with or without Congress .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Rather than force another unpopular and economically harmful government shutdown ,","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Trump sounds increasingly willing to accept the agreement in Congress","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that provides about $ 1.3 billion for border barriers .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"That ' s less than one-fourth of the $ 5.7 billion","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that he demanded initially for a wall .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"a point was made with the last shutdown , \"","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"the president said Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" People realized how bad the border is ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"how unsafe the border is . \"","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Lawmakers sorted out the details of the agreement","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"and released details of the bill early Thursday morning .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The House and Senate will be voting on the bill later in the day .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"The nearly 1,800-page spending bill has money for 55 miles of new border \" fencing \" in Texas , and money","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to maintain a daily average of 45,274 detention beds under Immigrations and Customs Enforcement , the agency","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"that now holds more than 49,000 immigrants","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"who live in the U.S. illegally in custody .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"The bill also provides the authority","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"to move cash around","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"to go above that level ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"if the Homeland Secretary determines","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"it ' s needed .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"When that question and others were still unresolved late Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"the conservative House Freedom Caucus called for a one-week extension of stopgap funding","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to keep the government open","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and give lawmakers more time","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to review the fine print of the border deal .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"Congress is facing a Friday deadline","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"to approve spending bills","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"to keep nine government agencies open .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"The agreement would pay for 55 miles of border fencing or barriers , but not concrete walls , in the Rio Grande Valley of Texas .","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"The president and his advisers are exploring other ways","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"to shift money within departments","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"to pay for more barriers ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"an option","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that is riling up congressional Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"\" He needs congressional permission","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to do it , \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"said Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"who noted","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that Democrats now hold the House majority .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"\" He doesn ' t have the authority","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to do it","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"without House permission . \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"But Republicans say","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"the law gives presidents some flexibility with so-called \" transfer authority \"","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to shift already-appropriated funds toward border security .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Sen. Roy Blunt of Missouri has cited as an example about $ 900 million","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"for fighting drug trafficking","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"that was appropriated to the Pentagon .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Trump is increasingly delivering the message","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"that he ' s already building the wall ,","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"regardless of Congress ,","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"he has \" options . \"","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"\" When people see what we ' re doing ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"they ' ll be very surprised , \"","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"\" We ' re doing a lot of work .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"We ' re giving out contracts right now .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"We have options","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that most people don ' t really understand . \"","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Speaking later Wednesday to law enforcement groups ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Trump vowed to \" finish the border wall . \"","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"\" As we review the new proposal from Congress ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"I can promise you this","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"I will never waver from my sacred duty","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to defend this nation and its people , \"","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"\" We will get the job done .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"It ' s happening . \"","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"He told police chiefs and county sheriffs","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"that the barrier will be \" a big wall . \"","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"\" It ' s a wall","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"that people aren ' t going through very easy , \"","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"the president said .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"\" You ' d have to be in extremely good shape","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"to get over this one .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"They would be able to climb Mount Everest a lot easier ,","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"I think . \"","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"The president ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"who vowed last December","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"that he would be \" proud \" to shut down the government over the principle of border security ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"made clear","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"that he doesn ' t want to repeat the episode","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"that forced 800,000 federal workers to go without pay for 35 days .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"\" A shutdown would be a terrible thing , \"","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"a lot of good points were made ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"but I don ' t want to see another one","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"- there ' s no reason for it . \"","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"While much of Mr. Trump ' s Republican base supported the shutdown","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"that started Dec. 22 ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"voters overall disapproved .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Gallup said Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that Mr. Trump ' s job-approval rating fell to 35 percent in mid-January during the shutdown ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"but had climbed back to 44 percent in early February","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"after he agreed to reopen the government .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"The increase was largely attributable to more-positive comments from independents ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"pollsters said .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"A Morning Consult/Politico survey","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"released Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"found that only 33 percent of respondents support a second shutdown over Mr. Trump ' s demand for a border wall .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Some influential conservatives aren ' t heaping as much public pressure on Mr. Trump this time","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"to force a shutdown .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Fox News host Sean Hannity called the new agreement a \" garbage compromise \"","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"when it came out Monday night ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"but he has since toned down his criticism ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"referring to the $ 1.3 billion as a \" down payment \" on the wall","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"and suggesting","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"the administration can find more money elsewhere in the federal budget .","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"\" In that case , he wins big time , \"","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"Mr. Hannity said on his daily radio show .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Critics of the president are saying","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"that he got nothing from the shutdown ,","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"because he got less for border barriers","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"than Democrats had offered last year .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"beginning with a campaign rally","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"he held Monday night on the border in El Paso , Texas ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Mr. Trump has been telling supporters","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"that the pain of the shutdown was necessary","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"to make his point about the urgency of the border security crisis .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"the shutdown was worth a temporary increase in the nation ' s unemployment rate .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"\" We had a little blip","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"[ in the unemployment rate ]","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"because of a thing","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"called the shutdown , \"","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"\" But remember this ...","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"if we didn ' t do that shutdown ,","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"we would not have been able to show this country , these politicians , the world , what the hell is happening with the border . \"","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"He added ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"\" That was a very important thing","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"we did . \"","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"White House aides also noted","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"that the agreement provides some money for border barriers ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"while House Speaker Nancy Pelosi had dismissively offered the president $ 1 for wall funding in testy talks during the shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi was urging House Democrats to support the tentative agreement Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"\" As with all compromises , I say to people ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"support the bill for what is in it , \"","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"\" Don ' t judge it for what is not in it .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"We have other days","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"to pass other legislation . \"","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"With lawmakers rushing to avoid another shutdown , however ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"some of the president ' s conservative allies were urging him to pack a short-term funding extension","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"to provide more time","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"to study the details of the deal .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"\" In politics trust is everything , \"","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"said Rick Manning , president of Americans for Limited Government .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"\" This president has no reason","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"to trust","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"that Speaker Pelosi did not insert trap language into the bill ,","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"and he would be wise to verify","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"that the proposed legislation is free from language","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"that would prevent meaningful action","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"to address the crisis at the border .","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"While everyone would like to see this drama finally come to an end ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"it is better to get it right","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"than to regret signing the bill later . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":339,"left":224,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":184,"right":223,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":174,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":172,"right":173,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":171,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":173,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":183,"left":178,"right":182,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":5,"right":177,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":177,"left":6,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":7,"right":175,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":180,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":179,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":181,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":203,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":200,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":200,"left":186,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":185,"right":17,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":194,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":189,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":18,"right